930349398.text: "Adenovirus mediated delivery of SOCS3 into cardiomyocytes was identified to suppress hypertrophic and anti-apoptotic phenotype induced by LIF mediated gp130 receptor signaling through Jak and Stat pathway, where LIF was also identified to induce Akt, MEK and ERK activation indicating that SOCS3 is induced by mechanical stress [XREF_BIBR]."
